Installation
# with yarn
yarn add @highlight-run/remix

Client Instrumentation
Inject <HighlightInit /> into your app root.Optionally configure excludedHostnames to block a full or partial hostname. For example, excludedHostnames={['staging']} would not initialize Highlight on staging.highlight.io.Configure tracingOrigins and networkRecording
